reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars SUCH A SPACE SAVER AND BEST DESIGN
reviews.reviewText: SUCH A SPACE SAVER AND BEST DESIGNThis is the best product for its price point and will repurchase.As a member of a family of 5 with limited home space, we have a lot of shoesWhat I love about this design of shoe tree is that there is a back panel and full bottom panel that contains any dirt that the shoes may have on them, but there is still openings on all sides where you can see what shoes you want from any direction. This is not just a good storage idea for shoes. I also store shoe inserts and callous and corn pads which do not fall out.I also made them one long line and it felt nice and durable but a bit wobbly. When I made it in two I felt a huge difference in the sturdiness. It's compact and just what I needed for the small space where I wanted it. Improvements that can be made: make a version that has a bit more space for work boots.I like how I have the option to make it as tall as I want so it can fit many different places and needs.Arrived on time, all parts were present, it was super easy to assemble, however, the actual product is smaller than what the pictures display.This is the best product for its price point and will repurchase.Very high qualityVery impressed
